import React from 'react'
import { BrowserRouter as Router, Route, Switch} from 'react-router-dom'
import Login from './Login'
import history from '../router/history'

const App = () => {
  return (
    <Router history={history}>
      <Switch>
        <Route path="/login" component={Login}/>
      </Switch>
    </Router>
  )
}

export default App
